stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Boot
    Boot --> Idle: shell initialized

    Idle --> MetaCommand: slash command
    Idle --> IntentRouting: natural-language input

    MetaCommand --> SessionReset: /clear
    MetaCommand --> Exit: quit or exit command
    MetaCommand --> Idle: other meta command handled

    SessionReset --> Idle: session cleared

    IntentRouting --> ClarifyingQuestion: ticker or intent ambiguous
    IntentRouting --> MemoryLookup: context may answer request
    IntentRouting --> FreshDataRetrieval: latest/current request or explicit refresh

    ClarifyingQuestion --> IntentRouting: user clarifies

    MemoryLookup --> ResponseRendering: saved context sufficient
    MemoryLookup --> FreshDataRetrieval: context stale or insufficient

    FreshDataRetrieval --> ResearchExecution: sources fetched
    FreshDataRetrieval --> ErrorRecovery: connector failure

    ResearchExecution --> Verification: outputs available
    ResearchExecution --> ErrorRecovery: execution failure

    Verification --> ResponseRendering: accepted or downgraded
    Verification --> ErrorRecovery: unrecoverable verification failure

    ResponseRendering --> Idle: response shown and state updated
    ErrorRecovery --> Idle: error surfaced and session preserved

    Exit --> [*]
